<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <title>Анализатор страниц</title>
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.7/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
              integrity="sha384-LN+7fdVzj6u52u30Kp6M/trliBMCMKTyK833zpbD+pXdCLuTusPj697FH4R/5mcr" crossorigin="anonymous">
    </head>
    <body class="min-vh-100 d-flex flex-column">
        <header class="flex-shrink-0">
            <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-dark bg-dark px-3">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Анализатор страниц</a>
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/">Сайты</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </header>
        <main class="flex-grow-1">
            <div class="container-lg mt-3">
                <h1></h1>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 col-md-10 mx-auto border rounded-3 bg-light p-5">
                        <h1 class="display-3">Анализатор страниц</h1>
                        <p class="lead">Бесплатно проверяйте сайты на SEO пригодность</p>
                        <form action="" method="post" class="row">
                            <div class="col-8">
                                <label for="text" class="visually-hidden">Url для проверки</label>
                                <input type="text" name="url[name]" value="" class="form-control form-control-lg" placeholder="https://www.example.com" required>
                                <div class="invalid-feedback"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-2">
                                <input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg ms-3 px-5 text-uppercase mx-3" value="Проверить">
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.7/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
                integrity="sha384-ndDqU0Gzau9qJ1lfW4pNLlhNTkCfHzAVBReH9diLvGRem5+R9g2FzA8ZGN954O5Q"
                crossorigin="anonymous">
        </script>
    </body>
</html>